500

, 500 , eigenvalue eigenvector .

theta<-rep(0,500)
evl<-matrix(0,nrow=500,ncol=5);
eig.res.tr<-eigen(tv)
for(i in 1:500){
A<-rmvnorm(100,mean=rep(0,10),sigma=tv)
scv<-cov(A)
eig.res<-eigen(scv)
theta[i]<-abs(t(eig.res$vectors[,1])%*%eig.res.tr$vectors[,1])
evl[i,]<-eig.res$values[1:5]
}
boxplot(evl)
x0s <- 1:5 - 0.5
x1s <- 1:5 + 0.5
y0s <- eig.res.tr$values[1:5]
segments(x0 = x0s, x1 = x1s, y0 = y0s, col = "red")

Review . .

\[ H = \left[ {\begin{array}{cc} A_{11} & A_{12} \\ A_{21} & D \end{array} } \right] \] \(A_{11} = 10 I_{10} + J_{10}, A_{12} = J_{10,n10} , D = 10 I_{n-10}\) . \(I_k\) \(k \times k\) , \(J_{l,m}\) \(l \times m\) 1 .

, \(H\)

\[ H^{-1} = \left[ {\begin{array}{cc} A_{11}^{-1}+A_{11}^{-1}A_{12}QA_{21}A_{11}^{-1} & -A_{11}^{-1}A_{12}Q \\ -QA_{21}A_{11}^{-1} & Q \end{array}} \right] \] (\(Q=D^{-1}+D^{-1}A_{21}(A_{11}-A_{12}D^{-1}A_{21})A_{12}D^{-1}\)) .
